y.view
Class TreeView

java.lang.Object
  y.view.TreeView
All Implemented Interfaces:
View
Deprecated. This class will be removed in future versions as it offers no relevant functionality. 

public class TreeView
extends Object
implements View

Shows the nodes of graph in a tree structure. This implementation is for flat graph structures only. For hierarchically nested graph structures Use HierarchyJTree instead.
